data.description: You have to see this perfectly kept 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in Cypress Bend! Large open living with lots of light, a cozy fireplace with a mantel and hearth. The living is open to the kitchen which has beautiful cabinetry, granite countertops, gas cooktop, large bar for seating, stainless appliances, a pantry and a wall oven and microwave. Very large laundry just off the kitchen with a sink, storage and room for an extra refrigerator or freezer! The primary suite is relaxing with its neutral wall tones and it leads to a tiled floor bathroom with a jetted tub, stall shower, dual sinks, and dual closets. There are two other bedrooms opposite of the home from the primary and the fourth bedroom is upstairs with a private bathroom. Flower beds have be redone and fresh mulch added. Covered patio in the fully fenced backyard. The roof, stucco and garage door all replaced in 2020. Great neighborhood and great school district!
